
Located in Dixon, Playland Centers was designed with the young family in mind and provides children with an enriching active and pretendplay environment to aid in their mental, social, emotional and physical development.

Playland has several themed play areas, including a Princess Boutique, Retro Diner, Pirates Cove, Market and Tot Spot. Playland also offers a used clothing retail outlet for gently used childrens and maternity clothing, a coffee bar, lounge seating, a variety of popular magazines, and living cheaply free Wireless Internet Wifi throughout the facility.
